'''Warp Effects''' are a feature, that plays a custom animation on a user when they enter or leave an [[Instances|instance]].

==Overview==
Warp Effects can be accessed in the Cosmetics section of the [[Inventory]] page. They can be acquired through, [[Bundles]], or the [[Shop]].

